C&W'S MOBILE AMBITIONS

Cable & Wireless aims to make 25 per cent of its earnings from mobile
communications by the year 2000, according to a presentation made by
the company to City analysts.  The company's investments include
cellular networks in the UK, France, Germany, Hong Kong, Japan and
South Africa.





